pageContext.claim: “Nancy Pelosi and the Democrats delayed the Workers Help/Stimulus Bill by over a week, trying to add real ‘junk’ into the Bill. Got some bad things, having nothing to do with those affected by the Virus, included. Republicans need their votes until we WIN BACK THE HOUSE IN 2020!”
pageContext.analysis: The covid-19 stimulus bill was negotiated in the Senate, not by Pelosi or the House. The House passed it two days after the Senate.
